!!!
%html.no-js{lang: "ru-RU"}
  %head
    %title Show / Offers / Fragrance
    = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/layouts/_head.haml')).render
  
  %body#page.page
    = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/common/_alerts.haml')).render
    = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/layouts/_header.haml')).render
    = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/layouts/_nav.haml')).render
    
    %main#main.main{role: "main"}
      = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/common/_breadcrumbs.haml')).render

      .ctn
        .p-t_3.p-b_4

          .grid
            
            .grid-i.__grid-7-24>
              %section.section.__margin.m-b_3{role: "region", "aria-label" => "Photo gallery"}
                .block.__normal
                  %img.va-t.c-bg.__gray{src: "/assets/images/fake/product-main-1.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "Lanvin"}

            .grid-i.__grid-17-24>
              %section.section.m-b_3{role: "region", "aria-label" => "Lanvin"}
                .block.__large.p-r
                  .offers-info
                    %a.offers-info_like{href: "#"}
                      %i.fa.fa-heart
                    %h1.offers-info_name.m-b_2 Lanvin
                    %h4.tx.__700.__upper.m-b_3 Парфюмированная вода Eclat d`arpege 30 мл.
                    %article.cnt.m-b_3
                      %p Парфюмерная вода Lanvin Eclat d`arpege&nbsp;&mdash; женственный и&nbsp;мягкий цветочный аромат. Пирамида начинается нотами лимонных листьев и&nbsp;сирени. Ноты сердца состоят из&nbsp;цветка персика, глицинии и&nbsp;зеленого чая. Базовый аккорд из&nbsp;мускуса и&nbsp;сладкой амбры.
                    .m-b_5
                      %div.m-b_1
                        %dl.grid
                          %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Цвет
                          %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Прозрачный
                      %div.m-b_1
                        %dl.grid
                          %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Страна производства
                          %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p ФРАНЦИЯ
                      %div.m-b_1
                        %dl.grid
                          %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Объем (мл) 
                          %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p 30
                      %div.m-b_1
                        %dl.grid
                          %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Сезон 
                          %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Мульти
                      %div
                        %dl.grid
                          %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Коллекция 
                          %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-3>
                            %p Весна-лето 2014

                    .grid
                      .grid-i.__grid-1-3.va-m>
                        %p.offers-price 
                          %span.format-money.__rub 1190
                      .grid-i.__grid-1-3.va-m>
                        %button.form-el.__btn.__green.grid-i.__grid-2-3 Купить


          .grid

            .grid-i.__grid-7-24>
              %section.section.__margin{role: "region", "aria-label" => "Brand information"}
                %h2.tx.__upper.m-b_2
                  Brand 
                  %span.tx.__400 information
                .block.__normal
                  .profile-contacts
                    %div.m-b_1
                      %dl.grid
                        %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p.tx.__right.__700 Country
                        %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p Russia
                    %div.m-b_1
                      %dl.grid
                        %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p.tx.__right.__700 Industry
                        %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p Fragrances 
                    %div.m-b_1
                      %dl.grid
                        %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p.tx.__right.__700 Designer
                        %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p
                            %a{href: "http://link.ac/kiT0"} link.ac/kiT0 
                    %div.m-b_1
                      %dl.grid
                        %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p.tx.__right.__700 Niche
                        %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p
                            %a{href: "http://link.ac/kiT0"} link.ac/kiT0 
                    %div
                      %dl.grid
                        %dt.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p.tx.__right.__700 Лицензия
                        %dd.grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                          %p LVMH

            .grid-i.__grid-17-24>
              %section.section.m-b_3{role: "region", "aria-label" => "Contact Information"}
                %h2.tx.__upper.m-b_2
                  Contact 
                  %span.tx.__400 Information
                .block
                  .p-t_3.p-b_3
                    %article.reviews-i
                      .grid
                        .grid-i.__grid-4-23.__prefix-1-23>
                          .reviews-i_user
                            = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/common/_avatar.haml')).render
                        .grid-i.__grid-17-23>
                          %header.m-b_2
                            .grid
                              .grid-i.__grid-3-4.va-m>
                                %h3.tx.__upper.__700 
                                  %a{href: "#"} Alexandra Klimov
                              .grid-i.__grid-1-4.va-m>
                                .tx.__right
                                  .stars.__readonly{data: {score: "#{rand(1..5)}"}}
                          %p I&rsquo;m really excited to&nbsp;share with you some concept app&nbsp;UI components based on&nbsp;iOS 7&nbsp;visual guidelines. Be&nbsp;sure to&nbsp;check out the full preview and don&rsquo;t forget to&nbsp;download the file.

              %section.section.m-b_3{role: "region", "aria-label" => "Feedback"}
                %h2.tx.__upper.m-b_2 Feedback
                .block
                  .p-t_3.p-b_3
                    - 1.upto(3) do
                      %article.reviews-i
                        .grid
                          .grid-i.__grid-4-23.__prefix-1-23>
                            .reviews-i_user
                              = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/common/_avatar.haml')).render
                          .grid-i.__grid-17-23>
                            %header.m-b_2
                              .grid
                                .grid-i.__grid-3-4.va-m>
                                  %h3.tx.__upper.__700 
                                    %a{href: "#"} Taylor Swift
                                .grid-i.__grid-1-4.va-m>
                                  .tx.__right
                                    .stars.__readonly{data: {score: "#{rand(1..5)}"}}
                            %p.m-b_1 Well, wish&nbsp;I could just paste Ouch&rsquo;s review here heh. Tested this again because it&nbsp;bothers me&nbsp;I don&rsquo;t like it&nbsp;as&nbsp;I adore most Prada scents. Nope. Eye swelling headache in&nbsp;a&nbsp;spray bottle. This is&nbsp;plastic caramel, there is&nbsp;nothing &laquo;Prada&raquo; about&nbsp;it. Not the dry down, not the start or&nbsp;middle. So&nbsp;linear, weak and straight up&nbsp;offensive.
                            %footer
                              .grid
                                .grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                                  %nav.reviews-i_action
                                    %a.reviews-i_action_i.__report{href: "#"}> Report
                                .grid-i.__grid-1-2>
                                  %p.tx.__s.__muted.__right 28 February 2014&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;11:20

              %section.section{role: "region", "aria-label" => "Products"}
                %h2.tx.__upper.m-b_2 Другие товары этого бренда
                .p-t_2.p-b_2
                  .grid
                    - 1.upto(8) do
                      .grid-i.__grid-1-4>
                        = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/common/_carousel_item_product_3.haml')).render

    = Haml::Engine.new(File.read('views/layouts/_footer.haml')).render